OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780567570
OL,3,CPolice watchdog urges public to 'stop
OL,4,Cspeculating' about Henry Nowak's murder
OL,6,FThe leader of the police watchdog has
OL,7,Furged people to stop speculating about
OL,8,Fthe murder of teenager Henry Nowak.
OL,10,FTensions have been rising since police
OL,11,Fbodycam footage released on Monday
OL,12,Fnight showed an officer handcuffing Mr
OL,13,FNowak as he lay dying from stab wounds.
OL,15,FThe footage was made public after
OL,16,FVickrum Digwa, 23, was jailed for life
OL,17,Ffor murdering the 18-year-old
OL,18,FUniversity of Southampton student with
OL,19,Fa Sikh ceremonial knife.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780567570
OL,3,CPolice watchdog urges public to 'stop
OL,4,Cspeculating' about Henry Nowak's murder
OL,6,FIndependent Officer for Police Conduct
OL,7,F(IOPC) Derrick Campbell said late on
OL,8,FWednesday: "We are acutely aware of
OL,9,Fthe public interest in this case.
OL,11,F"We would respectfully ask people to
OL,12,Fstop speculating on an ongoing live
OL,13,Finvestigation.
OL,15,F"This investigation is going to fully
OL,16,Festablish the circumstances of the
OL,17,Fcase including whether there may be
OL,18,Fmisconduct on the part of any of the
OL,19,Fofficers involved.
OL,26,@pD@LOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780567570
OL,3,CPolice watchdog urges public to 'stop
OL,4,Cspeculating' about Henry Nowak's murder
OL,6,F"The ongoing commentary about the
OL,7,Fevidence and speculation risks
OL,8,Fprejudicing any potential processes
OL,9,Fand preventing Henry Nowak's family
OL,10,Fgetting the answers they deserve."
OL,12,FNowak's death led to violent clashes
OL,13,Fwith police in Southampton on Tuesday
OL,14,Fnight, leaving 11 police officers and
OL,15,Fone police dog injured, according to
OL,16,FHampshire Police.
OL,18,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer told MPs
OL,19,Fon Wednesday that the violence was
OL,20,F"disgraceful and completely
OL,21,Funacceptable".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
