OL,3,CPolice watchdog urges public to 'stop
OL,4,Cspeculating' about Henry Nowak's murder
OL,6,FSpeaking outside court after the
OL,7,Fverdict on Monday, Mr Nowak's father,
OL,8,FMark, had said that his family wanted
OL,9,Fto use Henry's story "to make change
OL,10,Ffor the better" rather than as fuel
OL,11,Ffor conflict.
OL,13,F"We do not want his death to be used
OL,14,Fto create further division, hatred or
OL,15,Ftension. We want his story to help
OL,16,Fmake our streets safer for everyone,"
OL,17,Fhe said.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
