OL,3,CPolice watchdog urges public to 'stop
OL,4,Cspeculating' about Henry Nowak's murder
OL,6,FDespite pleas for calm, hundreds
OL,7,Fgathered outside Southampton Central
OL,8,FPolice Station shortly before 6pm on
OL,9,FTuesday, where Tommy Robinson and
OL,10,FLaurence Fox were among those who
OL,11,Fspoke to the crowd.
OL,13,FITV News Correspondent Neil Connery
OL,14,Freported live at the scene
OL,16,FViolent scenes broke out after a large
OL,17,Fgroup walked across town to the
OL,18,FPortswood area.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780567570
OL,3,CPolice watchdog urges public to 'stop
OL,4,Cspeculating' about Henry Nowak's murder
OL,6,FChairs, cans and flares were thrown at
OL,7,Fpolice in riot gear, eventually
OL,8,Fforcing officers and three police vans
OL,9,Fback from the line they had been
OL,10,Fholding.
OL,12,FThe National Police Chiefs' Council
OL,13,F(NPCC) said it would review anti-
OL,14,Fracism guidance ` which advises police
OL,15,Fto treat ethnic minorities differently
OL,16,Fto get them better outcomes ` that
OL,17,Fsome have blamed for the actions of
OL,18,Fthe officers who arrested Mr Nowak.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
