PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780567570
OL,3,CPolice watchdog urges public to 'stop
OL,4,Cspeculating' about Henry Nowak's murder
OL,6,FThe policing minister called the
OL,7,Flanguage in the document "clumsy" and
OL,8,Fadded, "it gives the wrong impression
OL,9,Fand needs to be changed".
OL,11,FThe Conservatives said "the race
OL,12,Faction plan needs to go" despite it
OL,13,Fbeing introduced while they were in
OL,14,Fgovernment.
OL,16,FDigwa was given a life sentence with a
OL,17,Fminimum of 21 years in prison for
OL,18,Fstabbing Mr Nowak with a ceremonial
OL,19,Fknife with a 21cm blade, prosecutors
OL,20,Fsaid was a kirpan, which he carried as
OL,21,Fpart of his Sikh religion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
