OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780567570
OL,3,CPolice watchdog urges public to 'stop
OL,4,Cspeculating' about Henry Nowak's murder
OL,6,FHe had previously been investigated by
OL,7,Fpolice in 2023 on suspicion of
OL,8,Fstealing ceremonial blades from a Sikh
OL,9,Ftemple in Southampton but no further
OL,10,Faction was taken.
OL,12,FEarlier on Tuesday, Hampshire Police
OL,13,Fsaid an officer not connected to the
OL,14,Fcase had faced death threats after
OL,15,Fbeing misidentified in online posts.
OL,17,FThe police watchdog is expected to
OL,18,Freport on the case within the next
OL,19,Fthree months.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
