OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780567570
OL,3,CPolice watchdog urges public to 'stop
OL,4,Cspeculating' about Henry Nowak's murder
OL,6,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,7,FConduct (IOPC) said its independent
OL,8,Finvestigation "remains ongoing".
OL,10,FIt added that investigators are
OL,11,Fexamining a large amount of body-worn
OL,12,Fvideo as well as material presented
OL,13,Fduring Digwa's trial.
OL,15,FHampshire Police confirmed that one of
OL,16,Fthe officers involved in the case has
OL,17,Fresigned, while the other three are
OL,18,Fstill serving. All of them are being
OL,19,Ftreated as witnesses.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
